<i>Joy is in the ears that hear!</i>
</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualexandrea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alexandrea</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.geocities.com/sryan02/eq/images/note.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#CC9900>(11/22/00 1:47:45 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   =)</span><hr size=1> Pixie works like a charm, call me the crowd control queen! haha <br>
<br>
In reality, yea it actually works now and I almost never got resisted with the pups in Karnor's when I was playing with it.<br>
<br>
But I was getting resisted with SoT even with my instrument... guess maybe I'm just not charming enough =) or maybe it's that kick-you at the begining of a level thing.. I'll keep trying it as I progress... <p><br>
